         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>The Uttirakāṇṭam is complete. The total of viruttams is 3762. On the meritorious day
               when the Jovian year Cittirapāṉu, month of Vaiyāci, 13th day, Sunday, the
               constellation of Rokaṇi fall together Cantiracekaraṉ Muttukkumaraṉ Kuruṉātaṉ fully
               copied and completed the Kūrmapurāṇam. The illustrious Ciṟṟampalam.</p>
         </div>
